data.title: Seiyuu Birthday
data.meta_description: Here is the list of seiyuu's birthday I've collected so far. Of course this is not a complete list. But I'll expand this further once I collect more and more data. January 2 - Toyoguchi Megumi (1978); Akesaka Satomi (1988); January 3 - Tanaka Rie (1978); January 5 - Sakuma Rei (1965); Asanuma Shintaro (1976);…
